{"tid":26049,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"[都市傳說] 北角七姊妹道","createTime":"2016-12-06T13:15:10.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-07T06:32:01.000Z","uid":7374,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"42ba61813161fa919734b34b9a2e8a51719855c3","tid":26049,"uid":7374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T13:15:10.000Z","msg":"相傳當地是一個客家人村落，當中有七位少女自幼成為總角之交，情同姊妹，於是她們結義金蘭，並立下「寧死不嫁」的誓言。 <br />\n<br />\n後來三妹的父母決定將她許配給同鄉，她卻不敢違抗父母之命。七位姊妹在她出嫁前一晚相聚痛泣，為遵守「寧死不嫁」以及「雖不能同年同月同日生，但願袛能同年同月同日死」的結拜誓詞，她們七人一起於當地海邊投海自盡。翌日，村民找不著她們的影蹤，但海灣出現了七塊礁石，形狀就如七位少女，他們認為由七姊妹所變成。這七塊礁石稱之為「七姊妹石」，而當地的村落亦改名為「七姊妹村」。 <br />\n<br />\n至1934年，香港政府於七姊妹區填海興建房屋，「七姊妹石」亦因此而長埋地底。"},{"pid":"9412b6c257c1aa3faf9db62707d42e81ba3b4e46","tid":26049,"uid":34999,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T13:18:10.000Z","msg":"avop-127"},{"pid":"68d6f33131bf34b15e9125d36f0876b82bc7dcf7","tid":26049,"uid":1884,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T13:22:26.000Z","msg":"住七姊妹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87b976176ac4a58fe39c07bf7fbad35afe0797d6","tid":26049,"uid":48088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T13:26:50.000Z","msg":"有趣地....英國倫敦都一樣有個地方叫七姊妹....<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://cdn.londonandpartners.com/asset/4688d93c6131ef85b4a764c57dd5709c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcdn.londonandpartners.com%2Fasset%2F4688d93c6131ef85b4a764c57dd5709c.jpg&h=a98d667d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"75f1305098e8a1e023354fabfef3d405336078bb","tid":26049,"uid":14497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T13:35:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有趣地....英國倫敦都一樣有個地方叫七姊妹....<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://cdn.londonandpartners.com/asset/4688d93c6131ef85b4a764c57dd5709c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcdn.londonandpartners.com%2Fasset%2F4688d93c6131ef85b4a764c57dd5709c.jpg&h=a98d667d&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n英國都有7姊妹一齊死"},{"pid":"6bf461a8db28c604ae44853121ebc473a6a8618e","tid":26049,"uid":54930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T14:14:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>avop-127</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9535b740f020dcf70fe88e5e80310c6d7294b97","tid":26049,"uid":34999,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T15:06:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>avop-127</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n識野喎清<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b89442e1578e05d4de4a73ed20c994d6517216fe","tid":26049,"uid":294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T15:18:06.000Z","msg":"雖然已經好耐<br />\n但個故事唔多可信<br />\n<br />\n除非7個都係肥婆"},{"pid":"f1f177fa9402b3d304bc651a09806056f10014bf","tid":26049,"uid":40233,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T15:23:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>住七姊妹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 健康邨？"},{"pid":"6193f34c29d45470dbf2fa1762b78d956e8496c7","tid":26049,"uid":45188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T16:24:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>有趣地....英國倫敦都一樣有個地方叫七姊妹....<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://cdn.londonandpartners.com/asset/4688d93c6131ef85b4a764c57dd5709c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcdn.londonandpartners.com%2Fasset%2F4688d93c6131ef85b4a764c57dd5709c.jpg&h=a98d667d&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n英國都有7姊妹一齊死</blockquote><br />\n英國Brighton都有Seven Sisters Country Park<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe76eb7e09eeca6149e531441bd7deb0d3ba7f4e","tid":26049,"uid":44